headline.print_headline: Fire Erupts Under New Jersey's Pulaski Skyway During Rebuilding
headline.main: Fire Erupts Under New Jersey's Pulaski Skyway During Rebuilding

lead_paragraph: Work on a project to rebuild New Jersey's crumbling Pulaski Skyway ground to a halt on Friday afternoon when a fire erupted along the supporting base of the elevated roadway that connects Jersey City and Newark, a state transportation official said.
